{"tid":1233674,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"現況就好似捉緊盤棋","createTime":"2019-06-16T20:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T07:15:19.000Z","uid":62811,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb80dafb434809c5bd675fc2b67611b5708c0ef","tid":1233674,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:18:24.000Z","msg":"當初警犬 政府成為公敵令全個社會大和解<br />\n依加對手向後行左步，態度無咁強硬自己友就開始亂，成晚都籠罩住內訌嘅氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n我無資格提出啲咩大方向同策略，或者形勢聽朝已經唔同，呢個post已經無存在價值，但今晚發生嘅事實在令我好擔心有機會重覆雨傘嘅錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n行到呢一步，我認為全靠香港人團結一致。喺未有任何下一步嘅對策前，老套啲我都係覺得<br />\n兄弟爬山 不篤灰 不割席，唔好比機會浪費義士嘅心血，以及生命。<br />\n<br />\n我想多謝大家到現時呢刻打左場略有少成 但喺代價極為沉重嘅仗，聽朝或者未來有更長遠嘅路要一齊行，無論成功與否，香港嘅前途靠哂各位香港人，香港加油！<br />\n<br />\n最後敬請各位小心行呢盤棋嘅下一步，唔好因為對手向後行左一步而我地不知所措。引用一句電影中嘅對白黎提醒大家，順便結束呢篇有感而發。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gmwgjdn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgmwgjdn.png&h=a3fa3e57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b442a53824cca6fa4e031b472e34bef7244f481","tid":1233674,"uid":237284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:19:59.000Z","msg":"最好既解就係保持團結力量 保持團堅持既火"},{"pid":"2558089acefec659e154dabc3460dd69de529f3d","tid":1233674,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:33:31.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"803f426d45775a4ed71abcef9ad206fbbd0e11bd","tid":1233674,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88deee3f279791acc217e510347ebbcc6535a2fe","tid":1233674,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T21:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f149f803a83bcbbbb626797553166a9c3f9a1d8a","tid":1233674,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:05:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"98d21c9d88a3b063a0c8b531fa111dc5dfe24497","tid":1233674,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}